                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.113/207: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Italy</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Child</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-12-23T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 23, 1921—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>203. Your 261 December 17, 2 p.m.</p>
                <p>You may separately but simultaneously with your British, French and Japanese
                    colleagues make representations suggested in your 258 December 13, 1 p.m.,
                    protesting to Italian Government against the <pb facs="0688" n="564"
                        xml:id="pg_564"/> handing over to the Military Governor of Chihli Province
                    arms which have been stored in Italian Barracks at Shanhaikuan.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
